<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <title>API JIRA</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.16.0/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
        <h2>API JIRA</h2>
        <p>En la siguiente tabla muestra el listado de tareas del sprint del proyecto :</p>
        <p>Inicia en: {{startAt}}, Cantidad de Resuldados: {{maxResults}}, Total: {{total}}</p>
        
        <table class="table table-striped table-condensed">
            <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Key</th>
                    <th>Nombre</th>
                    <th>Estado</th>
                    <th>Tipo</th>
                </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                {{#each list_task}}
                    <tr>
                    <td>{{this.key}}</td>
                    <td><a href="https://santex.atlassian.net/browse/{{this.key}}" target="_blank">{{this.summary}}</a></td>
                    <td>{{this.status}}</td>
                    <td>{{this.issuetype}}</td>
                    </tr>
                {{/each}}
                
            </tbody>
        </table>
    </div>

</body>

</html>